    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think this is due to the use of the `vm` module rather than the custom require. The `artifacts` global is injected into the context of the migration as run through `script.runInNewContext`, and it doesn't get propagated to submodules in the `require` function that is injected into that context.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/d26d7f46a3d38d4e42cd6317779575835830710d/packages/require/require.js#L91-L92\r\n\r\nI don't understand why `vm` is used in the first place so I'm not sure what kinds of fixes would be acceptable.",
